%% Data Flow Diagram: Llama Stack Distribution
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>kube-rbac-proxy
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant EmbeddingModel as Embedding Model<br/>(vLLM / local)
    participant VectorDB as Vector DB<br/>(Milvus/pgvector/Qdrant)
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI FMS<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant LMEval as TrustyAI LM Eval<br/>HTTP/K8s API
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Inference Request (vLLM Backend)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>LlamaStack: Forward (HTTP 8321)<br/>kube-rbac-proxy authenticated
    LlamaStack->>vLLM: POST inference request<br/>API Token auth
    vLLM-->>LlamaStack: Inference response
    LlamaStack->>PostgreSQL: Log inference<br/>Username/Password auth
    LlamaStack-->>Gateway: JSON response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: RAG Query with Vector Search
    Client->>LlamaStack: POST /v1/agents/* (RAG query)<br/>HTTP 8321
    LlamaStack->>EmbeddingModel: Generate embeddings<br/>API Token auth
    EmbeddingModel-->>LlamaStack: Embedding vectors
    LlamaStack->>VectorDB: Vector similarity search<br/>Token/Password auth
    VectorDB-->>LlamaStack: Relevant documents
    LlamaStack->>vLLM: LLM inference with context<br/>API Token auth
    vLLM-->>LlamaStack: Generated response
    LlamaStack->>PostgreSQL: Store agent state<br/>Username/Password auth
    LlamaStack-->>Client: RAG response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Safety-Guarded Inference
    Client->>LlamaStack: POST /v1/safety/*<br/>HTTP 8321
    LlamaStack->>TrustyAI: Content safety check<br/>TLS configurable (FMS_SSL_CERT_PATH)
    TrustyAI-->>LlamaStack: Safety verdict
    LlamaStack->>vLLM: Inference (if safe)<br/>API Token auth
    vLLM-->>LlamaStack: Response
    LlamaStack-->>Client: Guarded response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Model Evaluation (LM Eval)
    Client->>LlamaStack: POST /v1/eval/*<br/>HTTP 8321
    LlamaStack->>LMEval: Start evaluation job<br/>K8s ServiceAccount / HTTP
    LMEval->>vLLM: Inference requests<br/>API Token auth
    LMEval-->>LlamaStack: Evaluation results

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 5: Garak Security Benchmark (Kubeflow)
    Client->>LlamaStack: POST /v1/eval/* (Garak)<br/>HTTP 8321
    LlamaStack->>KFP: Create pipeline run<br/>API Token auth
    KFP->>LlamaStack: Benchmark requests<br/>HTTP 8321
    KFP->>S3: Store results<br/>AWS IAM / Access Keys
    KFP-->>LlamaStack: Benchmark results
    LlamaStack-->>Client: Evaluation response
